 ('1', '2929', 'en_us', 'You always come first', 'We always put the needs of families and students first. We represent no one’s interests but yours. Ever', '2017-01-26 20:14:15', '2017-01-26 23:47:39', 'ab25d968-b7b5-4247-aeac-5226fda9295d'),
